title: Biochemical Oxygen Demand
description:
Description
The BOD data frame has 6 rows and 2 columns giving the
biochemical oxygen demand versus time in an evaluation of water
quality.

parameters.Time: A numeric vector giving the time of the measurement (days).
parameters.demand: A numeric vector giving the biochemical oxygen demand (mg/l).
